rame URL","figmaUrlInputHelpText":"<b>How to find your frame URL:</b> In Figma Design, right click on the frame you want to import, then click \\"Copy/Paste as\\" and finally \\"Copy link to selection\\".","figmaUrlInputInvalid":"Invalid Figma URL. Please ensure link is a valid Figma frame for your connected account in the format https://www.figma.com/design/...","figmaUrlInputSubmit":"Attach to prompt","figmaUrlInputTitle":"Import Figma design","figmaUrlLabel":"Figma URL","grabAddToChrome":"Add to Chrome","grabAssetCount":"{count, plural, one {# Asset} other {# Assets}}","grabChromeExtension":"Chrome Extension","grabChromeMockupAlt":"Chrome Browser window showing the Replit extension in the sidebar","grabCreateApp":"Create app","grabEmptyDescription":"Grab any live webpage and spin up an editable version in Replit with just three clicks. Perfect for learning, remixing, or rapid prototyping. No manual setup, no copy-paste chaos, just instant creation.","grabEmptyHeadline":"Rebuild any webpage in Replit, instantly.","grabImportError":"Error: {message}","grabLoading":"Loading...","grabNoPageData":"No page data found","grabPageScreenshotAlt":"Page screenshot","grabScreenshotCount":"{count, plural, one {# Screenshot} other {# Screenshots}}","grabSomethingWentWrong":"Something went wrong","grabStageCreating":"Creating your app...","grabStageOpening":"Opening your new app!","grabStageReady":"Ready","grabStageUploading":"Uploading assets...","grabTryAgain":"Try Again","grabUntitledPage":"Untitled page","growthLearnMore":"Learn more","importDetectedBase44":"Base44 project detected, converting to a Replit App with full Agent support","importDetectedBolt":"Bolt project detected, converting to a Replit App with full Agent support","importDetectedLovable":"Lovable project detected, converting to a Replit App with full Agent support","importDetectedReplitAgent":"Previous Replit Agent project detected","importDetectedVercel":"Vercel project detected, converting to a Replit App with full Agent support","importNotCompatibleWithAgent":"This repo is not compatible with Agent. You can still manually edit the code or use AI Assistant.","importSourcePreviousReplit":"previous Replit project","limitedInputCountCharacters":"{current} / {max} characters","limitedInputCountNoLabel":"{current} / {max}","loggedOutCarouselNextSlide":"Next slide","loggedOutCarouselPreviousSlide":"Previous slide","loggedOutTestimonialDatabricks":"By integrating with Lakebase and Databricks Apps, we\'re combining Replit\'s capabilities with trusted enterprise data and governance, helping teams move from idea to production faster and more securely than ever.","loggedOutTestimonialGusto":"Replit Agent 4 is incredible. Its ability to take a one-shot prompt and flesh out the requirements before a full build is unmatched. It requires very little guidance to take a rough concept to a functional prototype. This makes my life as a Product Manager 10x easier. Rather than writing requirements and waiting for Figmas, I can show, not tell.","loggedOutTestimonialPayouts":"The parallel task execution is a game-changer for us. We have multiple builders working on the same codebase every day, and the ability to submit tasks simultaneously with full visibility before anything merges is exactly how we\'ve wanted to work. Agent 4 feels like it finally matches the speed our team actually operates at.","loggedOutTestimonialSmflDigitalLab":"Agent 4 is a game-changer. Multi-user vibe coding via the kanban is a significant milestone for enterprises. It\'s great for turning individual concepts into team realities and managing tasks through diverse role definitions.","loggedOutTestimonialTalkdesk":"To deliver the world\'s best customer experience, our internal teams need to work without limits. Replit gives our teams the \'superpowers\' to prototype and scale internal solutions in hours rather than weeks, ensuring our operations are as innovative as the products we build. We\'re excited to see what we can build with Agent 4.","loggedOutTestimonialZillow":"Agent 4 unlocks true collaboration and real-time learning — now our teams can design and build with our closest partners live, turn instant feedback into measurable wins, and deliver outcomes that delight customers and partners.","loggedOutTestimonialsEndorsedByInnovators":"Endorsed by innovators","loggedOutTestimonialsNextTestimonial":"Next<br></br>Testimonial","loggedOutTestimonialsPreviousTestimonial":"Previous<br></br>Testimonial","loggedOutTestimonialsTrustedByBuilders":"Trusted by builders","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltCandyGame":"iPhone showing a candy match-3 puzzle game with colorful sweets on a purple grid, Level 1 with shuffle button","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltFitness":"iPhone showing a fitness tracker app with daily stats displaying 1,840 calories and 4,521 steps, task list, and activity level chart","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltFood":"iPhone showing a dark-themed food tracking app with nutrition details for a Vegan Buddha Bowl displaying calories, protein, carbs, and fat","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltFrogGame":"iPhone showing a platform jumping game with a frog character bouncing on green platforms, score of 226","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltPiano":"iPhone showing a piano synthesizer app called THE REGENT with virtual keyboard, reverb, vibrato, resonance and tone controls","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltShowcase":"iPhone showing various apps built with Replit including games, productivity tools, and creative apps","mobileAppsPageExperienceAltSpanish":"iPhone showing a Spanish language learning app with a quiz asking how to say Good morning, with multiple choice answers","mobileAppsPageExperienceHeader":"Experience what\'s being built with Replit","mobileAppsPageExperienceSubtitle":"Real apps, created in Replit","mobileAppsPageFeaturesEverythingDescription":"Your app can do more than look good. Add user accounts, connect to AI, store data, and build the backend that powers it all—without juggling separate tools or services.","mobileAppsPageFeaturesEverythingTitle":"Everything your app needs","mobileAppsPageFeaturesRealMobileAppsDescription":"Build native apps that feel right at home on any phone. Use the camera, track location, and tap into all the features that make mobile apps powerful. Agent handles the technical details so your app runs smoothly on iOS devices.","mobileAppsPageFeaturesRealMobileAppsTitle":"Real mobile apps","mobileAppsPageFeaturesVibeCodeDescription":"Use the Replit iOS or Android app to vibe code websites and web apps with Agent on the go. To build a native iOS or Android app, open Replit on the web.","mobileAppsPageFeaturesVibeCodeTitle":"Vibe code from anywhere","mobileAppsPageStepsDescribeDescription":"Turn plain language into a native iOS app using Replit Agent. Generate real code, not prototypes.","mobileAppsPageStepsDescribeTitle":"Describe your idea","mobileAppsPageStepsHeaderAppReview":"The simplest way to go from prompt to an app that\'s ready for App Review","mobileAppsPageStepsHeaderDefault":"The simplest way to publish to live mobile apps","mobileAppsPageStepsPreviewDescription":"Instantly preview your app on a physical device using Expo and an auto-generated QR code. Iterate fast without manual setup.","mobileAppsPageStepsPreviewTitle":"Preview on your device","mobileAppsPageStepsPublishDescription":"Prepare and submit your app to the App Store and Google Play with guided steps. You\'ll still need a developer account—Replit streamlines everything else.","mobileAppsPageStepsPublishTitle":"Publish to the App Store","mobileAppsPageStepsSubmitDescription":"Replit prepares your app and walks you through submission to the App Store. You\'ll need an Apple Developer account, and your app will go through Apple\'s standard App Review before it\'s listed on the App Store.","mobileAppsPageStepsSubmitTitle":"Submit to the App Store","navMenuAccount":"Account","navMenuCommunityHub":"Community Hub","navMenuDevCopyUsername":"[dev] Copy Username","navMenuGetHelp":"Get help","navMenuHelp":"Help","navMenuLabel":"Menu","navMenuLogOut":"Log out","navMenuNotifications":"Notifications","navMenuPersonal":"Personal","navMenuProfile":"Profile","navMenuReadTheDocs":"Read the docs","navMenuSettings":"Settings","navMenuStatus":"Status","navMenuSwitchWorkspace":"Switch Workspace","navMenuTeamsSwitchError":"Something went wrong, please try again.","navMenuTheme":"Theme","navMenuThemeCustom":"Custom","navMenuThemeDark":"Dark","navMenuThemeLight":"Light","navMenuThemeSystem":"System","navMenuUsernameCopiedConfirm":"Username copied to clipboard","navMenuViewUpdates":"View updates","patchViewerBinary":"Binary","patchViewerBinaryNotShown":"Changes can\'t be shown for binary files.","patchViewerMoreChangesNotShown":"{count, plural, one {# more change not shown} other {# more changes not shown}}","patchViewerNoAdditionalChanges":"No additional changes","patchViewerOtherChangedNotShown":"{count, plural, one {# other changed file not shown} other {# other changed files not shown}}","patchViewerViewInFull":"view in full ({count, plural, one {# more changed file} other {# more changed files}})","patchViewerViewMoreChanges":"view {count, plural, one {# more change} other {# more changes}}","pricingAmountPerMonth":"{amount} / month","pricingBilledAnnually":"billed annually","pricingCompactSubtitle":"Designed for Every Stage","pricingCompactTitle":"Start Small. Scale Fast.","pricingCreditTierAria":"Credit tier","pricingPerMonth":"per month","pricingPeriodMonthly":"Monthly","pricingPeriodSaveAmount":"Save {amount}{suffix}","pricingPeriodYearly":"Yearly","pricingProMonthlyCredits":"{credits} monthly credits","referralCopyLink":"Copy link","referralCopyTooltip":"Copy referral link","referralEarnedAmount":"{amount} earned","referralNeedUsername":"You need a username to use the referral program.","referralShareOnSocials":"Share on Socials","referralShareOnXAria":"Share on X","referralTweetText":"Join me on Replit! Get {amount} in credits when you subscribe to a paid plan.","referralYourLink":"Your referral link","reloadBrokenBody":"You\'re on a version of the app that\'s having a bit of trouble, and there\'s a new version available! Reload now to avoid possible issues.","reloadBrokenButton":"Reload","reloadBrokenTitle":"Reload recommended","repoEmptyTrySelecting":"Try selecting a different account or organization.","repoImportedOn":"Imported on {date}","repoNoneFound":"No repositories found","repoOpen":"Open","repoShowMore":"Show more","repoUpdatedRelative":"Updated {date}","resourceUsageDeletedRepl":"Deleted Repl","resourceUsagePlusMore":"+{count} more","resourceUsageReplFallback":"Repl","commandBar.toolsLabel":"Tools","mobileAppsPageFaqAgentOnMobileAnswer":"Yes. You can use Replit Agent directly from the mobile app to build, iterate on, and publish web projects on the go. To work on a native iOS or Android app, open Replit on the web.","mobileAppsPageFaqAgentOnMobileQuestion":"Can I use Replit Agent on mobile?","mobileAppsPageFaqFreeToUseAnswer":"Yes, the Replit app is free to download and use. Your existing Replit account and plan work seamlessly across desktop and mobile.","mobileAppsPageFaqFreeToUseQuestion":"Is the Replit app free?","mobileAppsPageFaqHeading":"Frequently asked questions","mobileAppsPageFaqMobileAppAnswer":"Yes! Replit is available on both <ios>iOS</ios> and <android>Android</android>.","mobileAppsPageFaqMobileAppQuestion":"Is there a Replit mobile app?","mobileAppsPageFaqNativeMobileAppsAnswer":"Not today. The Replit mobile app is great for vibe coding websites and web apps with Agent on the go. Native iOS and Android app development (Expo Go previews, TestFlight builds, and App Store submissions) happens in Replit\'s web project editor.","mobileAppsPageFaqNativeMobileAppsQuestion":"Can I build a native mobile app inside the Replit app?","mobileAppsPageFaqOfflineSupportAnswer":"The Replit app requires an internet connection to sync your projects and access Replit services.","mobileAppsPageFaqOfflineSupportQuestion":"Does the app work offline?","mobileAppsPageFaqPlatformsAnswer":"The Replit app is available on <ios>iOS (App Store)</ios> and <android>Android (Google Play)</android>.","mobileAppsPageFaqPlatformsQuestion":"What platforms is it available on?","mobileAppsPageFaqPublishFromMobileAnswer":"Yes. You can build, preview, and publish web apps directly from the Replit app. To build a native iOS app and submit it to the App Store, open Replit on the web.","mobileAppsPageFaqPublishFromMobileQuestion":"Can I publish apps from my phone?","mobileAppsPageFaqSyncWithDesktopAnswer":"Yes. Your Repls, files, and settings sync automatically. Start a project on your computer and pick it up on your phone, or vice versa.","mobileAppsPageFaqSyncWithDesktopQuestion":"Do my projects sync between desktop and mobile?","mobileAppsPageFaqWhatCanIDoAnswer":"You can create new web projects, write and edit code, use Replit Agent, preview your web apps, collaborate with others, and manage your Repls — all from your phone or tablet.","mobileAppsPageFaqWhatCanIDoQuestion":"What can I do with the Replit app?","deleteModalAppNote":"Some Apps may take a few minutes to finish deleting.","deleteModalBody":"Are you sure you want to delete {target}? This cannot be undone.","deleteModalCancel":"Cancel","deleteModalConfirm":"Yes, delete {target}","deleteModalEntityFallback":"item","deleteModalEntityType":"{entityType, select, App {App} photo {photo} comment {comment} post {post} file {file} folder {folder} bucket {bucket} other {item}}","deleteModalThisEntity":"this {entityType}","deleteModalTitle":"Delete {target}?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildAndroidSupportAnswer":"You can build cross-platform apps for iOS and Android. You can publish to Google Play manually.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildAndroidSupportQuestion":"Is Android supported?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildMacXcodeAnswer":"No. Replit and Expo manage the build process for you in the cloud.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildMacXcodeQuestion":"Do I need a Mac or Xcode?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildNativeInIosAnswer":"Not today. The Replit iOS app is great for vibe coding websites and web apps with Agent on the go. Native iOS and Android app development (Expo Go previews, TestFlight builds, App Store submissions) happens in Replit\'s web editor.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildNativeInIosQuestion":"Can I build a native mobile app inside the Replit iOS app?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildPreviewWithoutAccountAnswer":"Yes. You can preview with Expo Go. You only need an Apple Developer account when you\'re ready to publish to TestFlight or the App Store.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildPreviewWithoutAccountQuestion":"Can I preview without an Apple Developer account?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildResponsiveVsNativeAnswer":"A mobile‑responsive web app is a website that adapts its layout in the browser. A React Native app is a native application installed on the device that uses platform APIs (camera, haptics, push notifications), offers better access to hardware and offline capabilities, and is distributed via app stores. Responsive web can be great for reach and zero‑install; native is best when you need device features, performance, or App Store distribution.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildResponsiveVsNativeQuestion":"How is this different from a mobile‑responsive web app?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildServersDatabasesAnswer":"Use Replit\'s built-in PostgreSQL, Object Storage, Connectors, and AI integrations—no separate infrastructure required.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildServersDatabasesQuestion":"What about servers and databases?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildWhatIsExpoAnswer":"Expo is what the Agent uses to build your mobile App on Replit. It is an open‑source platform and toolchain for building, running, and deploying cross‑platform native apps with React Native. Learn more at <expo>expo.dev</expo>.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildWhatIsExpoQuestion":"What is Expo?","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildWhatIsReactNativeAnswer":"React Native is an open-source framework from Meta for building native iOS and Android apps using React and JavaScript or TypeScript. It renders platform-native UI components (not a webview), so your app looks and feels native.","mobileAppsPageFaqBuildWhatIsReactNativeQuestion":"What is React Native?","mobileAppsPageFaqDisclosure":"Replit is not an app store and does not distribute apps directly to mobile devices. Apps built on Replit are submitted through Apple\'s App Review.","navMenuDesktopAppVersion":"Version {version}","pricingAccessToModels":"Access to {models}","pricingAdvancedModels":"Access to the most powerful models","pricingBuiltinDatabase":"Built-in database for full-stack apps","pricingCentralizedBilling":"Centralized billing","pricingCompanyProfile":"Publish a Company Profile to share your work","pricingContactSales":"Contact sales","pricingCoreDescription":"For personal projects & simple apps","pricingCreateMultimedia":"Create slides, videos, animations","pricingCreditsUpfrontAnnual":"Credits granted upfront with annual plan","pricingCustomGroups":"Custom groups","pricingCustomPricing":"Custom pricing","pricingCustomSeatLimits":"Custom seat limits","pricingDailyAgentCredits":"Free daily Agent credits","pricingDataRetention":"Database rollbacks for up to 28 days","pricingDataWarehouse":"Data warehouse connections","pricingDedicatedSupport":"Dedicated support","pricingDesignSystem":"Design system support","pricingEnterpriseDescription":"For enterprise-grade security & controls","pricingEverythingInPlan":"Everything in {plan}","pricingEverythingIncludedWith":"Everything included with Replit {plan}","pricingFaqAnnualDiscountAnswer":"Yes, you can select our annual plans when you checkout and they offer a discount compared to our monthly plans.","pricingFaqAnnualDiscountQuestion":"Do you offer annual plans at a discount?","pricingFaqBestPlanAnswer":"If you\'re building apps for personal use or starting to use Replit, we see customers choose our {corePlanName} plan. If you are ready to take it to the next level or work with a larger team, we see customers choose our {proPlanName} plan. If you need invoicing or Enterprise-level security & controls, we recommend you <contactLink>contact us</contactLink> to learn more about our Enterprise plan.","pricingFaqBestPlanQuestion":"What plan is best for me?","pricingFaqControlSpendAnswer":"You can set both custom alerts and budget limits to manage your costs and prevent unexpected charges. Usage alerts are a simple way to get a heads-up when you hit a certain spending amount beyond your monthly credits. Budgets are a hard cap on your monthly spending. Once your budget is met or exceeded, we will send you an email notification and temporarily suspend all of your usage-based services. See <spendLink>Managing Your Spend</spendLink> for more information.","pricingFaqControlSpendQuestion":"How can I control what I spend on Replit?","pricingFaqEffortBasedPricingAnswer":"As you use the Agent, you will spend credits. The Agent will spend more credits as it works longer, which means more complex requests will cost more than simple requests. This aligns the price you pay with the work performed and value you get. You can learn more <ebpLink>here</ebpLink>.","pricingFaqEffortBasedPricingQuestion":"What is Effort-Based Pricing (pay-as-you-go)?","pricingFaqFeaturesQuestion":"What are all the features included in these plans?","pricingFaqHeading":"Frequently asked questions","pricingFaqHowCreditsWorkAnswer":"Credits cover all your usage across Replit. They are used for building with Agent, publishing (hosting your app or automation on Replit), databases operations, and more. Each plan includes monthly credits ($20 for {corePlanName}, starting at $100 for {proPlanName}). Additional usage beyond your monthly credits is billed as pay-as-you-go using our <ebpLink>Effort-Based Pricing</ebpLink> model.","pricingFaqHowCreditsWorkQuestion":"How do credits work?","pricingFaqInvoicingAnswer":"Yes, for invoice-based billing, please <contactLink>contact us</contactLink> to learn more about the Enterprise plan.","pricingFaqInvoicingQuestion":"Do you offer invoicing instead of credit card payments?","pricingFaqRunOutCreditsAnswer":"You can either purchase a credit pack or you\'ll be charged for additional usage at pay-as-you-go rates. You can monitor your credit usage in your Usage page. Your monthly credits reset on your monthly renewal date.","pricingFaqRunOutCreditsQuestion":"What happens when I run out of credits?","pricingFaqSeeSpendingAnswer":"View costs for individual checkpoints in the Agent tab by hovering over the usage icon. You can also see detailed billing for a specific workspace or your whole account in Settings. Set up alerts and budgets to control spending there.","pricingFaqSeeSpendingQuestion":"How can I see how much I\'m spending?","pricingFaqStillHaveQuestions":"Still have questions?","pricingFaqStillHaveQuestionsBody":"You can see more details in our <billingLink>Billing docs</billingLink>. If you\'re interested in the Enterprise plan, <contactLink>contact us</contactLink>. For support, sign in to Replit and use the ? on the top right corner of the page for help.","pricingFaqSubscriptionIncludesAnswer":"You get access to the Replit platform, including a personal workspace, full Agent 3 access, <connectorsLink>Connectors</connectorsLink>, the ability to publish (host) your app, and more. When you subscribe to a Replit plan, you also receive monthly credits included in your subscription fee. {corePlanName} plan subscribers get $20 in monthly credits, while {proPlanName} subscribers get at least $100 in monthly credits. These credits cover all your usage across Replit—including building with Agent, publishing, databases operations, and more. Your credits reset each month. After you spend these initial credits, you will still be able to keep using Replit. You\'ll be charged for additional usage up to any usage budget you set.","pricingFaqSubscriptionIncludesQuestion":"What comes with my subscription?","pricingFreeDescription":"For exploring what’s possible","pricingFreePrice":"Free","pricingGetStarted":"Get started","pricingInviteCollaborators":"Invite up to {count, plural, one {# collaborator} other {# collaborators}}","pricingInviteViewers":"Invite up to {count, plural, one {# viewer} other {# viewers}}","pricingJoinPlanCta":"Join Replit {plan}","pricingMonthlyCredits":"{amount} of monthly credits","pricingParallelAgents10":"Work in parallel with up to 10 agents","pricingParallelAgents2":"Work in parallel with up to 2 agents","pricingPerUser":"per user","pricingPremiumSupport":"Premium support","pricingPrivacyControls":"Advanced privacy controls","pricingPrivateDeployments":"Publish private or password-protected deployments","pricingProDescription":"For commercial and professional builds","pricingPublish1Project":"Publish up to 1 project","pricingPublishAnyRegion":"Publish projects in any region","pricingRbac":"Role-based access control","pricingRegionSelection":"Region selection","pricingRemoveBadge":"Remove \\"Made with Replit\\" badge","pricingRolePermissions":"Role-based permissions for Apps and Deployments","pricingScim":"SCIM","pricingSignUpCta":"Sign up","pricingSingleTenant":"Single-tenant environments","pricingSsoSaml":"SSO / SAML","pricingStaticOutboundIps":"Static outbound IPs","pricingStoragePower":"5x more storage, 10x more power","pricingTeamsDescription":"Bring the power of Replit to your entire team.","pricingTeamsViewerSeats":"50 Viewer seats","pricingUnlimitedAppsEditors":"Create unlimited Apps with unlimited editors","pricingUnlimitedCreations":"Unlimited creations in a more powerful project editor","pricingUnlimitedWorkspaces":"Unlimited workspaces","pricingUpfrontCredits":"Upfront credits on annual plan","pricingUsageCreditsPerMonth":"{amount}/mo in usage credits included","pricingVpcPeering":"VPC peering","resourceUsageAdditional":"{value} additional {units}","resourceUsageMillions":"{value} million","resourceUsageUnitComputeHours":"compute hours","resourceUsageUnitComputeUnits":"compute units","resourceUsageUnitDays":"days","resourceUsageUnitDollars":"dollars","resourceUsageUnitEditRequests":"edit requests","resourceUsageUnitHours":"hours","resourceUsageUnitMinutes":"minutes","resourceUsageUnitPlanSteps":"plan steps","resourceUsageUnitRequests":"requests","resourceUsageUnitSite":"site","resourceUsageUnitTokens":"tokens","codeCopiedToast":"Copied!","codeCopyAlt":"Copy code to clipboard","codeInsertAlt":"Insert code at cursor","codeInsertedToast":"Inserted!","connectionBackToHome":"Back to home","connectionDevDetails":"Development connection details","connectionDismiss":"Dismiss","connectionErrorCode":"Error code: {code}","connectionInterrupted":"Your connection to Replit has been temporarily interrupted. Usually this is because of a network issue. Please refresh the page to continue.","connectionInterruptedMobile":"Your connection to Replit has been temporarily interrupted. If the issue continues please logout and re-login.","connectionPleaseRefresh":"Please refresh","connectionRefresh":"Refresh","connectionUrlPortMapping":"URL and port to service mapping","defaultBucketAccessAllow":"Allow for this Repl","defaultBucketAccessBody":"Do you want the App Storage bucket associated with your Dotfiles Repl to be accessible in this Repl? If your Dotfiles Repl has any secrets, they will be accessible to this Repl too.","defaultBucketAccessDeny":"Deny","defaultBucketAccessDenyNotice":"If you did not install the Replit dotfiles support, you should deny this.","defaultBucketAccessTitle":"Allow Dotfiles App Storage Bucket access","educationModalBack":"Back","educationModalGoToSlide":"Go to {title}","educationModalNavigation":"Navigation","gitInShellBody":"It looks like you\'re trying to connect to your {provider} repository. Authorize this session to use your credentials?","gitInShellConfirm":"Confirm for this session","gitInShellDeny":"Deny","gitInShellDenyNotice":"If you did not initiate a git command, you should deny this.","gitInShellRemoteGit":"remote Git","gitInShellTitle":"Pass {provider} Credentials","nixIsBrokenBackupNote":"Optionally, we can back up the broken configuration files and recover the original ones:","nixIsBrokenCheckFiles":"Check if your {dotReplit} and {replitNix} files are configured properly:","nixIsBrokenErrorMessage":"Error Message","nixIsBrokenFileContentsFailed":"failed recovering file contents","nixIsBrokenGitLogNotAccessible":"git log is not accessible","nixIsBrokenGitNotAccessible":"git is not accessible","nixIsBrokenRecoverButton":"Recover original configuration files","nixIsBrokenRecoveryFailed":"Recovery failed: {error}","nixIsBrokenTitle":"The nix environment failed to build","replDiagnosticsContainerId":"Container ID","replDiagnosticsCopyReplId":"Copy Repl ID","replDiagnosticsCopyToClipboard":"Copy to clipboard","replDiagnosticsLogs":"Logs","replDiagnosticsReplId":"Repl ID","replDiagnosticsReplIdLabel":"Repl ID: {replId}","replDiagnosticsSpecialPermissions":"You are seeing this functionality because you have special permissions.","replDiagnosticsTraces":"Traces","transferReplCancel":"Cancel","transferReplConfirm":"Yes, transfer this Repl","transferReplDescription":"Transfer this Repl to another account or organization.","transferReplNewOwner":"New Owner","transferReplNoPermission":"You do not have permission to transfer this Repl.","transferReplOwnershipWarning":"Transferring ownership might result in losing some features, depending on the subscription status of the selected organization. Click here for more details.","transferReplTitle":"Transfer {title}","transferReplToOrgBackgroundNote":"The transfer occurs in the background and may take some time to complete.","transferReplToOrgCancel":"Cancel","transferReplToOrgClose":"Close","transferReplToOrgConfirm":"Transfer to Workspace","transferReplToOrgDescription":"Select an organization to transfer \\"{title}\\" to. This action is irreversible and the app will no longer belong to you.","transferReplToOrgDestinationLabel":"Destination Organization","transferReplToOrgFailed":"Failed to transfer repl","transferReplToOrgLoadFailed":"Failed to load workspaces","transferReplToOrgNoOrgs":"You don\'t belong to any organizations. You need to be a member of an organization to transfer repls to it.","transferReplToOrgPlaceholder":"Choose a workspace...","transferReplToOrgSecretsWarning":"Linked account secrets will not be transferred. You\'ll need to re-link them in the destination workspace.","transferReplToOrgSelectAria":"Select workspace","transferReplToOrgSelectWorkspace":"Please select a workspace","transferReplToOrgStarted":"Successfully started transfer of \\"{title}\\" to {orgName}.","transferReplToOrgTitle":"Transfer {title} to Organization","transferReplToOrgTryAgain":"Failed to transfer repl. Please try again.","transferReplToOrgUnexpectedResponse":"Unexpected response from server","transferReplTypeName":"Type the name {name} to delete","unsupportedImage":"Unsupported image","budgetWarningLearnMore":"Learn more","budgetWarningNearingBody":"To prevent service suspension, consider increasing your limit or reducing usage.","budgetWarningNearingTitle":"Your usage is nearing your monthly cost limit.","budgetWarningReachedBody":"Increase your limit to resume normal functionality.","budgetWarningReachedTitle":"Your usage has reached your monthly cost limit.","commitTitleMerged":"merged","commitTitlePrLabel":"PR","commitTitleReverted":"reverted","commitTitleReverts":"reverts","creditsAccordionCreditPacks":"Credit packs","creditsAccordionPromotional":"Promotional credits","creditsBlockAmount":"{amount} {label}","creditsColumnExpiryDate":"Expiry date","creditsColumnIssueDate":"Issue date","creditsColumnName":"Name","creditsColumnUsage":"Usage","creditsEmpty":"You do not have any {label}","creditsLabelCreditPacks":"credit packs","creditsLabelGift":"gifted credits","creditsLabelReferral":"referral credits","creditsPurchaseCreditPack":"Purchase credit pack","