reate a completely empty project","emptyProjectLoadSourceError":"Could not load empty project source. Refresh and try again.","emptyProjectPrivateReplError":"You cannot create a private project in this workspace.","emptyProjectRenameHint":"You can rename the project title after creation.","emptyProjectReplLimitError":"You are at your app limit. Upgrade to create more apps.","fullReplitAgentSupportTooltip":"Full Replit Agent support","importFromBitbucket":"Import from Bitbucket","importFromProvider":"Import from {provider}","importGenericError":"Something went wrong, try again later.","importRepoTooBig":"This repository is too big to import. Choose another repository or upgrade to a subscription for more storage.","importRepoUnauthorized":"You do not have permission to access this repository. Please verify that you have access to this repository.","importRepoViolatesTos":"This repository possibly violates our Terms of Service. Contact support if you believe this is a mistake.","missingRepository":"Missing a repository?","noDescription":"No description","readyForImportPill":"Ready for Import","replNameLabel":"Repl name","replNamePlaceholder":"Enter repl name","seeOurDocsForFaqs":"See our docs for FAQs","selectDifferentRepo":"Select a different repo","selectedRepoLabel":"Selected Repo","sourceDetectedAs":"Source detected as {source}","enableZealotDescription":"Use the new Chateau agent experience","enableZealotLabel":"Enable Zealot agent","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign1Short":"Startup analytics dashboard","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign1":"A dashboard UI concept for a startup analytics tool displaying revenue, user growth, and engagement metrics","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign2Short":"Checkout flow prototype","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign2":"A clickable checkout flow prototype for an e-commerce clothing store to test the purchase experience with users","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign3Short":"Fitness app onboarding wireframe","oldExamplePromptMockupDesign3":"A wireframe for the onboarding flow of a personal fitness tracking app that introduces features like workout logging, goal setting, and progress tracking","oldExamplePromptWeb1Short":"B2B project management app","oldExamplePromptWeb1":"A project management web app for a small B2B SaaS startup team to track tasks, assign owners, set deadlines, and view progress across projects","oldExamplePromptWeb2Short":"Freelance client portal","oldExamplePromptWeb2":"A client portal for a freelance design business where customers can submit requests, upload files, and track the status of their projects","oldExamplePromptWeb3Short":"AI sales assistant","oldExamplePromptWeb3":"An AI sales assistant web app for a small SaaS company that drafts and sends personalized outreach emails to potential customers","oldExamplePromptSlides1Short":"Startup pitch deck","oldExamplePromptSlides1":"A startup pitch deck for a recycled clothing marketplace explaining the problem, solution, market opportunity, and business model","oldExamplePromptSlides2Short":"Quarterly review presentation","oldExamplePromptSlides2":"A quarterly review presentation for a SaaS startup team summarizing key metrics, wins, challenges, and next quarter priorities","oldExamplePromptSlides3Short":"Product launch presentation","oldExamplePromptSlides3":"A product launch presentation for a task management productivity app for small teams, covering features, development timeline, and go-to-market strategy","oldExamplePromptMobile1Short":"Weekly meal planner","oldExamplePromptMobile1":"A meal planning mobile app for busy college students that generates a weekly menu and automatically creates a grocery list","oldExamplePromptMobile2Short":"Beginner running tracker","oldExamplePromptMobile2":"A fitness tracking app for beginner runners that logs workouts, tracks distance and time, and shows monthly progress","oldExamplePromptMobile3Short":"Wellness journal","oldExamplePromptMobile3":"A journaling app focused on mental wellness with daily writing prompts, mood tracking, and a visual mood calendar","oldExamplePromptVideo1Short":"App signup demo","oldExamplePromptVideo1":"A step-by-step animated demo showing how users sign up and create their first project in a productivity app","oldExamplePromptVideo2Short":"Startup pitch explainer","oldExamplePromptVideo2":"An animated explainer video for a startup pitch illustrating the problem and the product solution","oldExamplePromptVideo3Short":"SaaS hero animation","oldExamplePromptVideo3":"A simple looping hero animation for a SaaS website homepage that shows team members collaborating on shared tasks","oldExamplePromptDataViz1Short":"Retail sales dashboard","oldExamplePromptDataViz1":"A sales dashboard for a retail company tracking revenue by region, month, and product category","oldExamplePromptDataViz2Short":"SaaS KPI dashboard","oldExamplePromptDataViz2":"A SaaS KPI dashboard showing user growth, churn rate, and retention trends over time","oldExamplePromptDataViz3Short":"Cohort analysis dashboard","oldExamplePromptDataViz3":"A cohort analysis dashboard that tracks how different user signup groups activate and retain over their first 30 days, with charts showing retention trends and activation rates","oldExamplePromptGame1Short":"3D puzzle platformer","oldExamplePromptGame1":"A 3D puzzle platformer where players solve environmental puzzles to unlock checkpoints and beat a level timer","oldExamplePromptGame2Short":"3D racing game","oldExamplePromptGame2":"A simple 3D racing game set on futuristic tracks with laps, speed boosts, and a leaderboard","oldExamplePromptGame3Short":"3D maze game","oldExamplePromptGame3":"A first-person 3D maze game where players collect hidden items while avoiding obstacles and earning points","oldExamplePromptDocument1Short":"Mobile app proposal","oldExamplePromptDocument1":"A project proposal for launching a new mobile app feature, including goals, timeline, resources, and budget","oldExamplePromptDocument2Short":"Messaging feature PRD","oldExamplePromptDocument2":"A product requirements document for a messaging feature in a collaboration app, outlining user stories and technical requirements","oldExamplePromptDocument3Short":"Meeting notes template","oldExamplePromptDocument3":"A meeting notes template for startup team meetings with sections for agenda items, decisions, and action items","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet1Short":"Student budget tracker","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet1":"A personal monthly budget tracker for a college student with spending categories and budget variance","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet2Short":"Sales pipeline tracker","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet2":"A sales pipeline tracker for a small B2B startup with deal owners, stages, and expected close dates","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet3Short":"Hiring tracker","oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet3":"A hiring tracker for a growing startup to track candidates, interview stages, feedback, and outcomes","examplePromptMockupDesign1Short":"Analytics dashboard mockup","examplePromptMockupDesign1":"Design a dashboard mockup for a SaaS analytics tool with a sidebar nav, KPI cards for MRR and churn, a revenue line chart, a signups-by-channel bar chart, and dark theme with blue accents","examplePromptMockupDesign2Short":"Checkout flow wireframe","examplePromptMockupDesign2":"Design a 4-step checkout wireframe for a sneaker store: cart review, shipping address form, payment selection with Apple Pay, and order confirmation with delivery estimate","examplePromptMockupDesign3Short":"Fitness app onboarding wireframe","examplePromptMockupDesign3":"Design a 5-screen mobile onboarding wireframe for a fitness app: welcome screen, goal selection, experience level picker, weekly schedule selector, and personalized plan preview","examplePromptMockupDesign4Short":"Social app profile design","examplePromptMockupDesign4":"Design a user profile page for a photo-sharing app with avatar, cover photo, bio, follower counts, a photo grid, story highlights row, and an edit profile button","examplePromptMockupDesign5Short":"Restaurant ordering UI","examplePromptMockupDesign5":"Design a mobile ordering UI for a poke bowl restaurant with a scrollable menu by category, item cards with photos and prices, a toppings customization sheet, and a sticky cart bar","examplePromptWeb1Short":"Project management app","examplePromptWeb1":"Build a project management app with a kanban board, task cards with assignees and due dates, a team calendar view, file attachments, and a time tracking toggle per task","examplePromptWeb2Short":"Freelance client portal","examplePromptWeb2":"Build a client portal for a freelance designer where clients submit briefs, upload reference files, view project status (draft, in review, approved), leave feedback, and download final files","examplePromptWeb3Short":"Designer portfolio site","examplePromptWeb3":"Make a portfolio site for a UI/UX designer with 6 mock case studies, an about page with bio, a services section, smooth scroll animations, and a contact form","examplePromptWeb4Short":"Recipe sharing platform","examplePromptWeb4":"Build a recipe sharing site where users post recipes with photos, tag by cuisine and dietary type, save favorites to a cookbook, and leave star ratings with comments","examplePromptWeb5Short":"Calorie tracking app","examplePromptWeb5":"Build a calorie tracking web app with a daily food log, food database search, a 2000-calorie goal, a macro breakdown pie chart, and a 30-day weight trend graph","examplePromptSlides1Short":"Startup pitch deck","examplePromptSlides1":"Create a 12-slide pitch deck for a secondhand clothing marketplace: market problem, how it works, traction metrics, business model (15% take rate), team bios, and a $2M seed ask","examplePromptSlides2Short":"Product launch presentation","examplePromptSlides2":"Create a product launch deck for an AI task management app targeting remote teams: the problem, product demo walkthrough, key features, pricing tiers, and launch timeline","examplePromptSlides3Short":"CPG brand pitch deck","examplePromptSlides3":"Create a pitch deck for a plant-based protein bar brand: market size, product line with 3 flavors, brand positioning vs. competitors, retail distribution strategy, unit economics, and funding ask","examplePromptSlides4Short":"Team onboarding slides","examplePromptSlides4":"Create an onboarding deck for new engineering hires: company mission, org chart, tech stack overview, dev workflow, key Slack channels, and a first-week setup checklist","examplePromptMobile1Short":"Meal planner app","examplePromptMobile1":"Build a weekly meal planner app with a drag-and-drop calendar, a recipe browser with quick-meals filter, auto-generated grocery lists by aisle, and a budget tracker for weekly food cost","examplePromptMobile2Short":"Running tracker app","examplePromptMobile2":"Build a running app with GPS route tracking, pace and distance stats, a couch-to-5K training plan, monthly mileage chart, and personal records for fastest mile and longest run","examplePromptMobile3Short":"Calorie counter app","examplePromptMobile3":"Build a calorie counting app where users scan barcodes to log food, set daily macro targets (protein, carbs, fat), view a donut chart of daily progress, and a 7-day intake trend line","examplePromptMobile4Short":"Habit tracker app","examplePromptMobile4":"Build a habit tracker app with a 30-day grid view per habit, customizable frequencies (daily, 3x/week), reminder notifications, weekly progress reports, and a streak counter","examplePromptMobile5Short":"Dog walking app","examplePromptMobile5":"Build a dog walking app where owners create a dog profile, browse nearby walkers with ratings and rates, book walks, track them on a GPS map, and leave reviews","examplePromptVideo1Short":"App signup demo","examplePromptVideo1":"Create a 60-second animated demo for a productivity app walking through signup, creating a project, adding team members, dragging tasks on a kanban board, and a free trial CTA","examplePromptVideo2Short":"Startup pitch explainer","examplePromptVideo2":"Create a 90-second explainer video for a pet insurance startup: worried pet owner at the vet, how the app works (snap a bill photo, get reimbursed), pricing, and a download CTA","examplePromptVideo3Short":"AI companion launch video","examplePromptVideo3":"Create a launch video for an AI companion app showing a voice conversation, the AI remembering past chats and preferences, switching between text and voice, ending with a tagline","examplePromptVideo4Short":"Fintech product walkthrough","examplePromptVideo4":"Create an animated walkthrough for a personal finance app: linking a bank account, spending dashboard, budget alerts, savings goals with progress rings, and a financial health score","examplePromptDataViz1Short":"Retail sales dashboard","examplePromptDataViz1":"Build a sales dashboard for a DTC candle company with KPI cards (revenue, orders, AOV), a monthly revenue chart, top products bar chart, a US sales map, and a recent orders table","examplePromptDataViz2Short":"SaaS KPI dashboard","examplePromptDataViz2":"Build a SaaS metrics dashboard with cards for MRR, growth rate, churn, and LTV, a stacked area chart of MRR by plan tier, a cohort retention heatmap, and new vs. churned customers chart","examplePromptDataViz3Short":"Cohort analysis dashboard","examplePromptDataViz3":"Build a cohort analysis dashboard with a retention heatmap (weekly cohorts vs. weeks since signup), color-coded cells, filters for plan type and signup source, and a line chart of best vs. worst cohorts","examplePromptDataViz4Short":"Marketing funnel dashboard","examplePromptDataViz4":"Build a marketing funnel dashboard: visits → signups → activated → paid conversions, with conversion rates between stages, a channel breakdown table, and a 90-day trend line per stage","examplePromptDataViz5Short":"Startup financial model","examplePromptDataViz5":"Build an interactive financial model with editable inputs for growth rate, burn rate, and starting cash. Show a 24-month cash projection chart, runway countdown, P&L table, and scenario toggle","examplePromptGame1Short":"3D puzzle platformer","examplePromptGame1":"Build a 3D puzzle platformer where a cube rolls across floating platforms, pushes blocks onto pressure plates, collects orbs for points, with a timer per level and star ratings. Low-poly pastel style","examplePromptGame2Short":"3D racing game","examplePromptGame2":"Build a 3D racing game with a hovercraft on a neon track, 3 laps per race, speed boost pads, a speedometer and lap timer HUD, obstacles, and a finish screen with best time. Synthwave palette","examplePromptGame3Short":"3D maze game","examplePromptGame3":"Build a first-person 3D maze game with procedurally generated mazes that grow each level, collectible keys, a minimap that reveals as you explore, a flickering torch, and a local leaderboard","examplePromptGame4Short":"Endless runner game","examplePromptGame4":"Build a 3D endless runner on a 3-lane highway: swipe to change lanes, jump over barriers, collect coins and power-ups, speed increases over time, with a high score and game-over screen","examplePromptGame5Short":"Tower defense game","examplePromptGame5":"Build a 3D tower defense game with 3 turret types at different price points, 10 waves of enemies, gold earned per kill, a base health bar, wave counter, and turret upgrade buttons","examplePromptDocument1Short":"DTC business plan","examplePromptDocument1":"Write a business plan for a DTC pet subscription box company: market opportunity, target customer profile, three pricing tiers, fulfillment plan, social media acquisition strategy, unit economics, and 12-month financial projection","examplePromptDocument2Short":"Messaging feature PRD","examplePromptDocument2":"Write a PRD for adding real-time group messaging to a project management app. Include user personas, user stories for threads, @mentions, file sharing, reactions, and search, plus technical requirements and a phased rollout plan","examplePromptDocument3Short":"API documentation","examplePromptDocument3":"Write API docs for a payments service with endpoints for charges, customers, subscriptions, and webhooks. Each endpoint should have method, URL, request body, example cURL, and response. Include auth and rate limiting sections","examplePromptDocument4Short":"Startup pitch memo","examplePromptDocument4":"Write an investment memo for a seed-stage AI tutoring startup: the problem, product overview, traction metrics, market size, team backgrounds, competitive landscape, and proposed seed round terms","examplePromptSpreadsheet1Short":"Startup financial model","examplePromptSpreadsheet1":"Build a financial model for a seed-stage SaaS startup with editable inputs for growth rate, MRR, churn, and burn. Show a 24-month projection of revenue, expenses by category, net burn, cash balance, and runway","examplePromptSpreadsheet2Short":"Sales pipeline tracker","examplePromptSpreadsheet2":"Build a sales pipeline spreadsheet with columns for deal name, company, owner, stage, value, probability, expected close date, and next action. Include a summary with total pipeline, funnel chart, and win rate","examplePromptSpreadsheet3Short":"Inventory tracker","examplePromptSpreadsheet3":"Build an inventory spreadsheet for a small e-commerce store: product name, variant, stock level, reorder point, cost, retail price, and margin. Highlight low-stock items in red and include a total inventory value summary","examplePromptSpreadsheet4Short":"Event planning budget","examplePromptSpreadsheet4":"Build an event budget spreadsheet for a 200-person conference with line items for venue, catering, A/V, speakers, and marketing. Each row has budgeted vs. actual columns, and a summary with a spending pie chart","orgTemplateDatabricksAppDisabled":"Requires a Databricks integration","orgTemplateDatabricksAppLoading":"Checking integration…"}')},933333,(e,t,a)=>{t.exports={openingApp:"Opening Repli