nt to be kept secret that let other services (Slack apps, CI pipelines, status dashboards etc) reach your app without signing in. These tokens are for API usage only (e.g. curl, fetch, server-to-server calls). They are not intended for accessing UI pages from a browser session.","projectProtectionBypass.advancedPill":"Advanced","projectProtectionBypass.envFieldLabel":"Environment","projectProtectionBypass.envDevelopment":"Development","projectProtectionBypass.envProduction":"Production","projectProtectionBypass.envHintDevelopment":"Authenticates against your workspace dev URL (.replit.dev). Useful while wiring up integrations before publishing.","projectProtectionBypass.envHintProduction":"Authenticates against your published deployment (.replit.app). Requires the App to be published.","projectProtectionBypass.emptyState":"You haven\'t created any access tokens yet.","projectProtectionBypass.loadMore":"Load more","projectProtectionBypass.unlabeled":"Unlabeled","projectProtectionBypass.activeMeta":"Created {createdAt} · Expires {expiresAt}","projectProtectionBypass.expiredMeta":"Expired {date}","projectProtectionBypass.revokedMeta":"Revoked {date}","projectProtectionBypass.createButtonShort":"Create access token","projectProtectionBypass.createButton":"Create access token","projectProtectionBypass.createTitle":"Create external access token","projectProtectionBypass.createDescription":"Generate a token that lets outside services (Slack apps, CI pipelines, status dashboards, etc.) access your deployment without signing in. Treat it like a password — anyone with it can reach your app. The token is shown once, then only its label and expiration are visible.","projectProtectionBypass.createUnknownError":"Could not create access token. Please try again.","projectProtectionBypass.labelFieldLabel":"Label (optional)","projectProtectionBypass.labelFieldPlaceholder":"e.g. laptop, CI","projectProtectionBypass.labelTooLong":"Label must be {max} characters or fewer.","projectProtectionBypass.durationFieldLabel":"Expires after","projectProtectionBypass.durationFieldHint":"Expires {date}.","projectProtectionBypass.duration1h":"1 hour","projectProtectionBypass.duration24h":"24 hours","projectProtectionBypass.duration7d":"7 days","projectProtectionBypass.duration30d":"30 days","projectProtectionBypass.duration3mo":"3 months","projectProtectionBypass.duration1y":"1 year","projectProtectionBypass.duration5y":"5 years","projectProtectionBypass.cancel":"Cancel","projectProtectionBypass.revealTitle":"Copy your external access link","projectProtectionBypass.revealTitleTokenOnly":"Copy your external access token","projectProtectionBypass.revealWarning":"Copy this link now — we won\'t show it again. Treat it like a password: anyone with it can reach your app until it expires or is revoked.","projectProtectionBypass.revealWarningTokenOnly":"Copy this token now — we won\'t show it again. Treat it like a password: anyone with it can reach your app until it expires or is revoked.","projectProtectionBypass.revealLabelPrefix":"Label: {label}","projectProtectionBypass.bypassQueryParamLabel":"Query parameter","projectProtectionBypass.copyBypassQueryParam":"Copy query parameter","projectProtectionBypass.bypassQueryParamHint":"Append this query parameter to non-UI API endpoint URLs. For browser-facing URLs, Vite apps serve a separate JavaScript bundle on a second request that won\'t include the parameter, causing that request to fail.","projectProtectionBypass.tokenCopied":"Copied","projectProtectionBypass.bypassLinkLabel":"Access link","projectProtectionBypass.bypassTokenLabel":"Access token","projectProtectionBypass.copyBypassLink":"Copy link","projectProtectionBypass.copyBypassToken":"Copy token","projectProtectionBypass.bypassLinkHint":"Preview is truncated — \\"Copy link\\" copies the full URL. Share it to let outside traffic reach your app without signing in; access ends when the link expires or is revoked.","projectProtectionBypass.bypassTokenHintIntro":"We couldn\'t auto-generate a link for this deployment. Send this token with every request using one of:","projectProtectionBypass.bypassTokenHintQueryParam":"• Append ?project-protection-bypass={placeholder} to your deployment URL.","projectProtectionBypass.bypassTokenHintHeader":"• Or send an Authorization: Bearer {placeholder} header.","projectProtectionBypass.bypassTokenHintSecrecy":"Access ends when the token expires or is revoked.","projectProtectionBypass.copyRawTokenAction":"Copy token only (for API / Bearer headers)","projectProtectionBypass.copyRawToken":"Copy the raw token","projectProtectionBypass.bearerHeaderHint":"Set this HTTP header on every request. Most HTTP clients (curl, fetch, axios) accept an Authorization header directly.","projectProtectionBypass.done":"I\'ve saved my link","projectProtectionBypass.doneTokenOnly":"I\'ve saved my token","projectProtectionBypass.revokeAlt":"Revoke access token","projectProtectionBypass.revokeTitle":"Revoke external access token","projectProtectionBypass.revokeWarning":"Are you sure you want to revoke {identifier}? Any traffic using this link will immediately lose access.","projectProtectionBypass.revokeDescription":"Revocation cannot be undone. If you need access again, you can create a new access token.","projectProtectionBypass.revokeConfirm":"Revoke access token","projectProtectionBypass.revokeSuccess":"Access token revoked","projectProtectionBypass.revokeUnknownError":"Could not revoke access token. Please try again.","projectProtectionBypass.unnamedLink":"this access token","deployToDatabricks":"Deploy to Databricks","databricksSubheading":"This app will be deployed to Databricks infrastructure.","statusPaused":"Paused","statusSuspended":"Suspended","statusUpdatingTier":"Updating tier","statusPausing":"Pausing","statusResuming":"Resuming","statusProvisioning":"Provisioning","statusBuilding":"Building","statusSecurityScanning":"Security scanning","statusBundling":"Bundling","statusPromoting":"Promoting","stat